Class DownloadCommandDetails

java.lang.Object
  com.serena.dmclient.api.TransferCommandDetails
      com.serena.dmclient.api.DownloadCommandDetails

public class DownloadCommandDetails
extends TransferCommandDetails

This is used to specify the command details. the flag values are Booleans so that if not set the corresponding parameter to the download command will not be passed.
